      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in exemplary condition. This vehicle features the high-strung S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies, delivering a seamless power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, this unit is flawless: the dual-VANOS system has been professionally bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced to ensure structural integrity. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. Every component, from the rod bearings to the suspension geometry, remains in factory-spec or better condition. This is a rare opportunity to own a mechanically perfect analog icon.",
