      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, and the exterior reflects that level of care with a deep, mirror-like finish, zero stone chips, and a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the original factory scent is still present. Every mechanical component has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a comprehensive binder of every service record included. From the flawless alloy wheels wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber to the untouched undercarriage, this vehicle presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. It has never seen rain, has never been smoked in, and has been handled with enthusiast-level care since day one. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key example that requires absolutely nothing but a new garage.",
